DIGEST
SB 23 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Boudreaux
Present law defines "food service establishment" for purposes of regulation by the La. Dept.
of Health.
Present law provides for exemptions to the definition.
Proposed law adds "adult residential care provider" to the list of exemptions.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Adds R.S. 40:5.5(E)(2)(j))
